(
<figureCitation id="09D4F6EFFF86FF96FD8CFC54FD33B9B0" box="[598,680,943,967]" captionStart="FIGURE 11" captionStartId="23.[151,250,1923,1946]" captionTargetBox="[158,1435,1045,1901]" captionTargetId="figure-415@23.[158,1436,1045,1901]" captionTargetPageId="23" captionText="FIGURE 11. Distribution of Belomitra species. Type locality of Belomitra decapitata is marked with an arrow. For Belomitra granulata, B. reticulata, B. subula, and B. brachytoma, distribution areas and types localities are figured, not the individual collection sites." pageId="23" pageNumber="24">Fig. 11</figureCitation>
